00:01:26.803 --> 00:01:30.140 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Do you know what time it is?

00:01:30.140 --> 00:01:34.010 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Most of us are conscious of time every day.

00:01:34.010 --> 00:01:38.848 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
We have a time to go to work,
a time to go to school, a time to eat,

00:01:38.848 --> 00:01:41.551 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
a time for our Christian meetings,

00:01:41.551 --> 00:01:44.487 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and even a time for association

00:01:44.487 --> 00:01:46.756 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
with our dear friends.

00:01:46.756 --> 00:01:49.125 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
As the Great Timekeeper,

00:01:49.125 --> 00:01:53.463 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Jehovah reminds us at Ecclesiastes 3:1

00:01:53.463 --> 00:01:57.433 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
that there is a proper “time for everything.”

00:01:57.433 --> 00:02:00.537 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
And thus, it’s not surprising
that the Bible speaks

00:02:00.537 --> 00:02:04.140 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
of the right time for various events.

00:02:04.140 --> 00:02:08.545 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
For example, at Leviticus 26:4,

00:02:08.545 --> 00:02:11.881 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Jehovah promised the obedient Israelites

00:02:11.881 --> 00:02:16.753 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
that he would bless them
with “showers of rain at [the] proper time.”

00:02:16.753 --> 00:02:20.089 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Well, that’s just a detail, probably,
for most of us.

00:02:20.089 --> 00:02:22.659 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
But if you’ve ever lived
in a farming community

00:02:22.659 --> 00:02:24.961 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
or you’ve done farming yourself,

00:02:24.961 --> 00:02:28.364 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
you know that rain at the right time

00:02:28.364 --> 00:02:31.401 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
can give you a bumper crop,

00:02:31.401 --> 00:02:33.536 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
but rain at the wrong time

00:02:33.536 --> 00:02:37.974 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
can completely destroy that same crop.

00:02:37.974 --> 00:02:41.044 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Even words can be spoken at the right time.

00:02:41.044 --> 00:02:44.047 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Proverbs 15:23 says:

00:02:44.047 --> 00:02:46.783 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“A word spoken at the right time

00:02:46.783 --> 00:02:49.819 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
—how good it is!”

00:02:49.819 --> 00:02:53.223 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Truly, it is a fundamental principle

00:02:53.223 --> 00:02:56.659 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
that timing is everything.

00:02:56.659 --> 00:03:00.263 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Well, think for a moment
about prophesied events

00:03:00.263 --> 00:03:03.066 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
that took place right on time.

00:03:03.066 --> 00:03:07.503 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Jesus was baptized at precisely the time

00:03:07.503 --> 00:03:10.473 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
when the Messiah was prophesied to appear.

00:03:10.473 --> 00:03:13.710 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
The Kingdom began its heavenly rule

00:03:13.710 --> 00:03:17.313 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
right on time in 1914.

00:03:17.313 --> 00:03:20.416 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
And looking to the future, Jesus said

00:03:20.416 --> 00:03:22.485 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
that Jehovah has set the time,

00:03:22.485 --> 00:03:26.489 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
even the exact day and the hour,

00:03:26.489 --> 00:03:30.093 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
for the end of this wicked system of things.

00:03:31.160 --> 00:03:34.264 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Does the Governing Body know

00:03:34.264 --> 00:03:36.866 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
when Armageddon is going to come?

00:03:38.368 --> 00:03:40.870 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Yes, we do.

00:03:40.870 --> 00:03:44.140 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
It’s going to come right on time.

00:03:45.575 --> 00:03:48.177 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
We have full confidence in that
—don’t we?—

00:03:48.177 --> 00:03:52.782 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
that Jehovah is going to bring about
those earth-shaking events

00:03:52.782 --> 00:03:55.885 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
exactly on time.

00:03:55.885 --> 00:03:59.122 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
But there is something else
that Jehovah has promised

00:03:59.122 --> 00:04:01.124 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
to provide at the proper time.

00:04:01.124 --> 00:04:02.926 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Would you go to your Bibles?

00:04:02.926 --> 00:04:07.797 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Let’s look at Matthew chapter 24

00:04:07.797 --> 00:04:09.799 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and verse 45.

00:04:13.603 --> 00:04:16.306 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Now, here Jesus posed this question:

00:04:16.306 --> 00:04:20.243 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“Who really is
the faithful and discreet slave

00:04:20.243 --> 00:04:23.546 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“whom his master appointed
over his domestics,

00:04:23.546 --> 00:04:26.716 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“to give them their food

00:04:26.716 --> 00:04:30.086 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“at the proper time?

00:04:30.086 --> 00:04:32.655 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“Happy is that slave if his master

00:04:32.655 --> 00:04:35.591 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“on coming finds him doing so!

00:04:35.591 --> 00:04:38.628 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“Truly I say to you, he will appoint him

00:04:38.628 --> 00:04:41.731 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
over all his belongings.”

00:04:41.731 --> 00:04:43.967 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Well, what did Jesus say here?

00:04:43.967 --> 00:04:48.137 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
He said that he would appoint
a “faithful and discreet slave”

00:04:48.137 --> 00:04:50.540 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
who would provide the spiritual food.

00:04:50.540 --> 00:04:54.777 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
But there is another important detail there
—did you notice it?

00:04:54.777 --> 00:04:59.782 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
He added “at the proper time.”

00:04:59.782 --> 00:05:04.420 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Well, because of Jehovah’s
perfect sense of time,

00:05:04.420 --> 00:05:08.291 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
he knows exactly what his people need

00:05:08.291 --> 00:05:13.296 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and he knows exactly the right time
to provide it.

00:05:13.296 --> 00:05:17.567 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Now, just consider
 a couple of examples of this.

00:05:17.567 --> 00:05:21.070 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Just as World War II was erupting,

00:05:21.070 --> 00:05:25.074 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
the November 1, 1939, issue of <i>The Watchtower</i>

00:05:25.074 --> 00:05:27.844 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
featured an in-depth discussion

00:05:27.844 --> 00:05:30.913 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
of the topic of neutrality.

00:05:30.913 --> 00:05:35.485 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
That timing was absolutely perfect.

00:05:35.485 --> 00:05:37.754 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Because of those articles,

00:05:37.754 --> 00:05:40.256 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
our brothers worldwide

00:05:40.256 --> 00:05:43.359 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
knew exactly what to do

00:05:43.359 --> 00:05:48.264 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
as the war engulfed the entire planet.

00:05:48.264 --> 00:05:53.269 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Well, after the war
as the organization was rapidly growing,

00:05:53.269 --> 00:05:55.371 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Jehovah’s organization arranged

00:05:55.371 --> 00:05:59.142 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
large international conventions

00:05:59.142 --> 00:06:01.277 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
that were held in New York City.

00:06:01.277 --> 00:06:06.282 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
In 1958, a quarter of a million people
—can you imagine?—

00:06:06.282 --> 00:06:09.552 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
overflowed Yankee Stadium
and the Polo Grounds.

00:06:09.552 --> 00:06:11.554 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Were any of you there?

00:06:12.655 --> 00:06:15.825 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Well, it’s so wonderful that we still have
a few people who were there.

00:06:19.062 --> 00:06:21.898 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
It’s not that I wasn’t
in the truth at that time;

00:06:21.898 --> 00:06:24.700 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
it’s just that I wasn’t
in the world at that time.

00:06:26.469 --> 00:06:29.672 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Well, that amazing convention

00:06:29.672 --> 00:06:32.508 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
came just on time.

00:06:32.508 --> 00:06:36.946 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
It energized God’s people
and, we could say,

00:06:36.946 --> 00:06:41.150 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
it put Jehovah’s Witnesses on the map.

00:06:41.150 --> 00:06:44.053 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
It was hard to ignore a convention

00:06:44.053 --> 00:06:47.890 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
of a quarter of a million people.

00:06:47.890 --> 00:06:51.761 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Well, fast forward to 2020

00:06:51.761 --> 00:06:54.931 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
at a time when the world was engulfed

00:06:54.931 --> 00:06:57.433 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
in a global pandemic.

00:06:57.433 --> 00:07:00.803 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Large gatherings were prohibited
in most countries.

00:07:00.803 --> 00:07:03.406 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Could we go to Yankee Stadium and have

00:07:03.406 --> 00:07:06.075 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
250,000 people there?

00:07:06.075 --> 00:07:07.643 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
No.

00:07:07.643 --> 00:07:09.812 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
But right on time,

00:07:09.812 --> 00:07:13.249 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Jehovah guided
“the faithful and discreet slave”

00:07:13.249 --> 00:07:15.485 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
so that our worldwide brotherhood

00:07:15.485 --> 00:07:19.255 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
could enjoy the convention program from home

00:07:19.255 --> 00:07:22.558 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
—truly, spiritual “food

00:07:22.558 --> 00:07:25.294 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
at the proper time.”

00:07:25.294 --> 00:07:29.932 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
And during the pandemic, we’ve had
to change our methods, haven’t we?

00:07:29.932 --> 00:07:34.303 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
We’ve had to receive direction
about how to carry out our preaching work

00:07:34.303 --> 00:07:37.173 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and how to carry out
our congregation meetings.

00:07:37.173 --> 00:07:39.942 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
But throughout this period, we have received

00:07:39.942 --> 00:07:43.012 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
powerful, powerful evidence

00:07:43.012 --> 00:07:48.017 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
that Jehovah has given this direction to us
at the proper time.

00:07:48.017 --> 00:07:50.987 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Now, let me just give you
a couple of examples.

00:07:50.987 --> 00:07:57.059 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
During the 2021 service year,

00:07:57.059 --> 00:08:00.229 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
at least 22 branches

00:08:00.229 --> 00:08:05.268 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
have reported an all-time peak
in the number of publishers.

00:08:05.268 --> 00:08:08.571 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Can you imagine—during the pandemic?

00:08:08.571 --> 00:08:12.074 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
For example, the Korea branch

00:08:12.074 --> 00:08:15.411 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
has reported a new peak in publishers

00:08:15.411 --> 00:08:20.016 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
every month during the 2021 service year.

00:08:20.016 --> 00:08:23.119 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Isn’t that amazing—during a pandemic?

00:08:31.594 --> 00:08:34.830 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
And with so many wonderful things
happening in the field,

00:08:34.830 --> 00:08:36.832 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
I’m sure that you’re all wondering

00:08:36.832 --> 00:08:40.636 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
about our worldwide Memorial attendance

00:08:40.636 --> 00:08:43.773 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
for 2021.

00:08:43.773 --> 00:08:46.609 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Well, by the undeserved kindness

00:08:46.609 --> 00:08:49.078 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
of our amazing God, Jehovah,

00:08:49.078 --> 00:08:52.949 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
we have reached an all-time peak,

00:08:52.949 --> 00:08:57.920 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
crossing the 21 million mark.

00:08:57.920 --> 00:09:00.556 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Would you like to know the exact figure?

00:09:05.628 --> 00:09:07.630 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Well, “keep on the watch”!

00:09:07.630 --> 00:09:10.633 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
It’ll be announced today at the proper time.

00:09:13.636 --> 00:09:15.905 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Well, today in our program,

00:09:15.905 --> 00:09:18.708 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
we are going to have a wonderful buffet

00:09:18.708 --> 00:09:23.679 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
of rich spiritual food
of many varieties and types.

00:09:23.679 --> 00:09:27.717 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
And by the end of the program,
I’m sure that you’ll agree

00:09:27.717 --> 00:09:30.720 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
that it was just what we needed

00:09:30.720 --> 00:09:33.289 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
at this moment in time.

00:09:34.357 --> 00:09:37.426 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Well, last year at the 2020 annual meeting,

00:09:37.426 --> 00:09:39.996 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
the Governing Body was excited to release

00:09:39.996 --> 00:09:44.100 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
a new publication to study
with interested ones entitled

00:09:44.100 --> 00:09:49.105 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
<i>Enjoy Life Forever!</i>
<i>—An Interactive Bible Course</i>.

00:09:49.105 --> 00:09:52.608 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
It introduced a new and innovative way

00:09:52.608 --> 00:09:55.645 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
to study the Bible with interested ones.

00:09:55.645 --> 00:09:58.814 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
How has the publication
been received by Jehovah’s people?

00:09:58.814 --> 00:10:00.816 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
And maybe more to the point,

00:10:00.816 --> 00:10:03.886 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
How is this new format touching the hearts

00:10:03.886 --> 00:10:06.689 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
of those studying the Bible with us?

00:10:06.689 --> 00:10:09.025 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Please enjoy this video.

00:10:18.034 --> 00:10:19.869 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
How thrilled we were

00:10:19.869 --> 00:10:21.637 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
at last year’s annual meeting

00:10:21.637 --> 00:10:23.773 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
to receive a new publication:

00:10:24.473 --> 00:10:28.377 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
<i>Enjoy Life Forever!</i>
<i>—An Interactive Bible Course </i>!

00:10:28.911 --> 00:10:31.747 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Already many publishers are having success

00:10:31.747 --> 00:10:35.384 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
in conducting progressive studies
using this new tool.

00:10:36.752 --> 00:10:39.789 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
As you listen to experiences
from around the world,

00:10:39.789 --> 00:10:43.559 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
note the evidence of Jehovah’s blessing.

00:10:44.393 --> 00:10:45.895 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
When they made the announcement

00:10:45.895 --> 00:10:47.229 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
of the new publication,

00:10:47.229 --> 00:10:49.832 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
for me it was just pure excitement.

00:10:49.832 --> 00:10:51.467 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
Actually, I was so overjoyed

00:10:51.467 --> 00:10:53.502 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
that I kept going to the website

00:10:53.502 --> 00:10:55.304 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
around the time of the release,

00:10:55.304 --> 00:10:57.573 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and at times I would even refresh my browser

00:10:57.573 --> 00:11:00.109 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
a few times a day to see when it was out.

00:11:00.109 --> 00:11:02.144 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
Having all the teaching methods

00:11:02.144 --> 00:11:03.512 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
right in our hands

00:11:03.512 --> 00:11:05.381 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
—what more can we ask for?

00:11:05.381 --> 00:11:08.818 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
We were so excited that during this pandemic,

00:11:08.818 --> 00:11:10.653 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
Jehovah has given us something

00:11:10.653 --> 00:11:12.421 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
to energize our ministry.

00:11:13.956 --> 00:11:18.794 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
When you heard that we would be using
a new method for conducting studies,

00:11:18.794 --> 00:11:21.030 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
were you a bit hesitant?

00:11:21.030 --> 00:11:24.133 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Pay close attention
to what experienced teachers are saying

00:11:24.133 --> 00:11:26.802 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
about the benefits of this approach.

00:11:28.137 --> 00:11:30.139 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
Before, it wasn’t uncommon

00:11:30.139 --> 00:11:32.174 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
to hear students start their comments

00:11:32.174 --> 00:11:34.543 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
with expressions like “the paragraph says”

00:11:34.543 --> 00:11:36.045 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
or “as the book mentions.”

00:11:36.045 --> 00:11:37.413 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Now it’s not like that.

00:11:37.413 --> 00:11:39.548 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
In the old way of teaching,

00:11:39.548 --> 00:11:41.951 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
it was a bit difficult for me to discern

00:11:41.951 --> 00:11:44.153 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
if my Bible students really understood

00:11:44.153 --> 00:11:48.157 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
what they were learning
or if the truth reached their hearts.

00:11:48.157 --> 00:11:49.725 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
I think I was using

00:11:49.725 --> 00:11:51.160 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
too many additional points

00:11:51.160 --> 00:11:52.628 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
to convey one idea

00:11:52.628 --> 00:11:54.497 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
and just explaining too much,

00:11:54.497 --> 00:11:58.501 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
so my Bible students
would get even more confused.

00:11:59.235 --> 00:12:01.537 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
With some well-educated people,

00:12:01.537 --> 00:12:03.339 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
the studies were in a sense

00:12:03.339 --> 00:12:05.074 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
too easy for them.

00:12:05.074 --> 00:12:08.544 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
They found the answer very easily
from the paragraph

00:12:08.544 --> 00:12:11.313 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and were able to answer correctly,

00:12:11.313 --> 00:12:14.750 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
but it was very hard to know
what they really thought about the matter.

00:12:15.851 --> 00:12:17.853 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
With this new book,

00:12:17.853 --> 00:12:19.855 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
it seems like it is easier to see

00:12:19.855 --> 00:12:23.759 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
the person’s genuine thoughts on the matter.

00:12:23.759 --> 00:12:25.928 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
In the previous method,

00:12:25.928 --> 00:12:27.930 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
you would see the student

00:12:27.930 --> 00:12:30.433 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
looking at the book a lot,

00:12:30.433 --> 00:12:32.701 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
but that doesn’t happen now.

00:12:32.701 --> 00:12:34.703 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
When you look at the student,

00:12:34.703 --> 00:12:38.073 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
you can tell he is thinking about the answer

00:12:38.073 --> 00:12:40.276 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
instead of looking for the answer.

00:12:41.177 --> 00:12:44.046 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
They used to enjoy
the Bible study in the past,

00:12:44.046 --> 00:12:48.083 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
but now they enjoy it much more.

00:12:48.083 --> 00:12:50.453 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Now they are able to keep focused

00:12:50.453 --> 00:12:54.123 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
from the beginning to the end of our session.

00:12:54.123 --> 00:12:58.360 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
They feel motivated and closer to Jehovah.

00:13:00.129 --> 00:13:02.465 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
To reach the heart of a Bible student,

00:13:02.465 --> 00:13:05.868 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
we need to understand
what he’s thinking and feeling.

00:13:06.569 --> 00:13:10.072 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
How does the <i>Enjoy Life Forever!</i>  book
help us to do that?

00:13:11.073 --> 00:13:13.075 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
One of the things I love about it

00:13:13.075 --> 00:13:15.110 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
is how after we read the Bible verse,

00:13:15.744 --> 00:13:17.813 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
there are the questions that follow it

00:13:17.813 --> 00:13:19.882 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
that are perfectly phrased for us.

00:13:19.882 --> 00:13:22.051 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
It really engages our students’ hearts,

00:13:22.051 --> 00:13:24.053 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and it helps them to understand

00:13:24.053 --> 00:13:26.055 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
the Bible teachings right away,

00:13:26.055 --> 00:13:28.591 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and it helps us to see
what’s in their heart as well.

00:13:28.991 --> 00:13:30.993 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
It lets the student express

00:13:30.993 --> 00:13:32.761 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
what is in his heart,

00:13:32.761 --> 00:13:35.097 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
which allows us to help him.

00:13:35.397 --> 00:13:37.132 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
The first time I looked

00:13:37.132 --> 00:13:38.501 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
through this publication,

00:13:38.501 --> 00:13:39.668 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
I could already see

00:13:39.668 --> 00:13:41.837 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
how appealing its format is.

00:13:41.837 --> 00:13:43.839 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
There are no lengthy paragraphs,

00:13:43.839 --> 00:13:46.642 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and it is prepared in a very interactive way.

00:13:48.511 --> 00:13:51.013 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
With this new method, I definitely talk less.

00:13:51.013 --> 00:13:52.748 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
My students talk more.

00:13:53.415 --> 00:13:55.417 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
And the one that starts it all off

00:13:55.417 --> 00:13:57.353 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
—the introduction video—

00:13:57.353 --> 00:13:59.922 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
just makes everything fit together.

00:13:59.922 --> 00:14:01.924 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
And one of the amazing things

00:14:01.924 --> 00:14:05.327 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
that it introduces right away is the prayer,

00:14:05.327 --> 00:14:08.364 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
because often as a teacher,
we didn’t know exactly

00:14:08.364 --> 00:14:10.833 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
when to introduce prayer or how to do it,

00:14:10.833 --> 00:14:12.835 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
but the video does it for us.

00:14:26.715 --> 00:14:30.786 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Obviously, teachers are excited
about the new book.

00:14:30.786 --> 00:14:34.490 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
But what impact
is it having on their students?

00:14:35.491 --> 00:14:36.792 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
Bible students

00:14:36.792 --> 00:14:38.794 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
have been pleasantly surprised.

00:14:38.794 --> 00:14:41.063 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
I asked one student how he felt

00:14:41.063 --> 00:14:43.732 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
to be using this new publication.

00:14:43.732 --> 00:14:45.734 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
And the response was:

00:14:45.734 --> 00:14:48.203 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“Why didn’t we do this sooner?

00:14:48.203 --> 00:14:51.106 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
It’s great!
I’m a lot calmer.”

00:14:51.106 --> 00:14:53.542 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Another student
told me that she was relieved

00:14:53.542 --> 00:14:55.644 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
to no longer have to find the answers

00:14:55.644 --> 00:14:58.147 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
but, rather, to express
her thoughts and feelings.

00:14:59.148 --> 00:15:00.649 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
During our discussion

00:15:00.649 --> 00:15:02.885 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
of the “Dig Deeper” section in lesson 02,

00:15:02.885 --> 00:15:05.154 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
my Bible student really appreciated

00:15:05.154 --> 00:15:08.157 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
the scriptures and the beautiful artwork.

00:15:09.258 --> 00:15:12.261 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
He said that he
could already see himself in Paradise

00:15:12.261 --> 00:15:14.730 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
enjoying the many promises of Jehovah.

00:15:14.730 --> 00:15:17.066 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
He said that our discussion

00:15:17.066 --> 00:15:20.502 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
made him feel Jehovah’s love.

00:15:20.502 --> 00:15:21.670 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
With the students,

00:15:21.670 --> 00:15:23.973 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
they’re not so overwhelmed with the new book

00:15:23.973 --> 00:15:26.008 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
when we ask them to prepare the lesson.

00:15:26.008 --> 00:15:28.444 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
With the <i>Bible Teach</i>  book,
when we would ask them

00:15:28.444 --> 00:15:30.746 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
to prepare these paragraphs,

00:15:30.746 --> 00:15:32.381 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
it was like you asked them
to go to the dentist.

00:15:32.381 --> 00:15:34.516 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
They just seemed so intimidated by it.

00:15:34.516 --> 00:15:38.954 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
But now they smile, and they’re like,
“OK, I can do that.”

00:15:38.954 --> 00:15:40.956 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
One student in particular

00:15:40.956 --> 00:15:42.992 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
wrote in the “Goal” box:

00:15:42.992 --> 00:15:44.693 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
“I want to share the points

00:15:44.693 --> 00:15:46.095 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“from this lesson

00:15:46.095 --> 00:15:48.597 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
with my friends and work colleagues
within a week.”

00:15:48.597 --> 00:15:50.032 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
And he did.

00:15:50.866 --> 00:15:53.202 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
One of the videos that was really effective

00:15:53.202 --> 00:15:55.204 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
was the one from lesson 04,

00:15:55.204 --> 00:15:57.206 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
<i>My Search for the True God</i>.

00:15:57.206 --> 00:16:00.476 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
It shows the experience
of Sister Soten Yoeun.

00:16:00.476 --> 00:16:02.578 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
My students were deeply moved.

00:16:03.479 --> 00:16:06.215 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
They really felt Jehovah’s love for them

00:16:06.215 --> 00:16:08.417 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and wanted to speak with him.

00:16:08.417 --> 00:16:11.286 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
They felt motivated to pray.

00:16:11.954 --> 00:16:15.591 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
We were studying the first lesson
with an 83-year-old lady

00:16:15.591 --> 00:16:19.228 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
when we came across Matthew 7:7.

00:16:21.163 --> 00:16:23.666 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
She read it in her own Bible,

00:16:23.666 --> 00:16:26.635 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and at first she didn’t quite understand it.

00:16:29.605 --> 00:16:32.508 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Then we pondered over the verse
together with the question.

00:16:32.508 --> 00:16:35.444 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
And then all of a sudden she asked:

00:16:35.444 --> 00:16:37.780 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“Oh! Does this verse mean

00:16:37.780 --> 00:16:40.449 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“that I should dig
for the answers in the Bible myself

00:16:40.449 --> 00:16:43.919 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
instead of asking a priest?”

00:16:43.919 --> 00:16:46.422 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
It was quite a special moment.

00:16:47.089 --> 00:16:48.290 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
The video

00:16:48.290 --> 00:16:50.693 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
under “Learn to enjoy Bible reading”

00:16:50.693 --> 00:16:53.128 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
was very helpful for one young man.

00:16:53.128 --> 00:16:54.663 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
After watching it,

00:16:54.663 --> 00:16:58.333 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
he set the goal
of reading the Bible every day.

00:16:59.234 --> 00:17:00.636 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
With one Bible student,

00:17:00.636 --> 00:17:03.038 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
we had encouraged him
to become an unbaptized publisher

00:17:03.038 --> 00:17:05.941 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
in the previous study book.

00:17:05.941 --> 00:17:10.112 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
And now when we were in lesson 02
of our new study publication,

00:17:10.112 --> 00:17:14.116 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
he expressed the desire
to become an unbaptized publisher

00:17:14.116 --> 00:17:18.620 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
because he felt he could share
one or two points from each lesson

00:17:18.620 --> 00:17:21.590 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
with his friends and others that he knew.

00:17:21.590 --> 00:17:25.260 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
And so now he is approved,
and he’s doing very well in the ministry.

00:17:25.260 --> 00:17:30.232 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Thanks to this new book,
I now conduct 15 Bible studies.

00:17:30.232 --> 00:17:33.802 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
The book helps them to maintain
the desire and motivation

00:17:33.802 --> 00:17:35.804 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
to keep learning about Jehovah,

00:17:35.804 --> 00:17:39.374 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
his beautiful qualities,
and the future that awaits us.

00:17:40.876 --> 00:17:44.780 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Clearly,
our worldwide brotherhood is excited

00:17:44.780 --> 00:17:47.750 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
to use <i>Enjoy Life Forever! </i>

00:17:47.750 --> 00:17:50.886 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
What a tremendous gift from Jehovah!

00:17:50.886 --> 00:17:53.522 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Of all the facets of our ministry,

00:17:53.522 --> 00:17:55.157 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
without question

00:17:55.157 --> 00:17:57.760 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
conducting a progressive Bible study

00:17:57.760 --> 00:18:00.329 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
is the most satisfying aspect.

00:18:00.329 --> 00:18:01.930 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
And now we have the tool

00:18:01.930 --> 00:18:03.966 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
and the method to make it much easier.

00:18:03.966 --> 00:18:06.168 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
I’m very grateful for this tool.

00:18:06.168 --> 00:18:08.604 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
It really helps us to sense

00:18:08.604 --> 00:18:10.706 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
how close the Governing Body

00:18:10.706 --> 00:18:13.342 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
recognizes we are to the end,

00:18:13.342 --> 00:18:16.311 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
but it in no way feels like a rushed program.

00:18:16.311 --> 00:18:19.782 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
The heart is definitely
being reached gently and lovingly,

00:18:19.782 --> 00:18:22.651 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
but then that is what motivates quickly.

00:18:22.651 --> 00:18:24.520 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Try and introduce it as much as you can.

00:18:24.520 --> 00:18:26.555 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Start those Bible studies.

00:18:26.555 --> 00:18:28.524 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
And when you do,

00:18:28.524 --> 00:18:30.692 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
please invite me
to join in on your new Bible study.

00:18:42.671 --> 00:18:44.640 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
The new book <i>Enjoy Life Forever! </i>

00:18:44.640 --> 00:18:46.875 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
shows clearly
that “the faithful and discreet slave”

00:18:46.875 --> 00:18:50.879 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
has been, is, and will continue to give

00:18:50.879 --> 00:18:54.249 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
exactly what we need
at exactly the right time.

00:18:54.917 --> 00:18:57.886 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
This publication has the potential

00:18:57.886 --> 00:19:00.255 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
to help many more honesthearted ones

00:19:00.255 --> 00:19:04.326 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
come to know and love
our wonderful Father, Jehovah.

00:19:04.326 --> 00:19:07.930 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
May he bless you and your Bible students

00:19:07.930 --> 00:19:10.232 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
as you put to use this new tool.

00:19:23.545 --> 00:19:26.548 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Well, that was very, very encouraging,

00:19:26.548 --> 00:19:31.186 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and we apologize to all those
who work in the dental office.

00:19:31.186 --> 00:19:33.589 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
We do appreciate your hard work.

00:19:34.356 --> 00:19:38.727 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Well, no doubt many of you
are experiencing similar blessings

00:19:38.727 --> 00:19:41.997 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
as you are conducting Bible studies
in this wonderful new tool.

00:19:41.997 --> 00:19:45.868 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
If you are not presently conducting
a Bible study,

00:19:45.868 --> 00:19:49.972 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
why not make it a matter
of earnest prayer to Jehovah?

00:19:49.972 --> 00:19:52.074 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Because there is no experience

00:19:52.074 --> 00:19:56.445 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
quite like having a Bible study
in this wonderful new publication.

00:19:57.579 --> 00:19:59.815 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Well, for the past several years,

00:19:59.815 --> 00:20:02.851 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
a unique feature
of our annual meeting program

00:20:02.851 --> 00:20:06.355 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
