00:20:06.355 --> 00:20:09.424 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
of the <i>Become Jehovah’s Friend</i>  series.

00:20:09.424 --> 00:20:14.429 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
We call it an epic because it is longer
than the usual episodes.

00:20:14.429 --> 00:20:16.465 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
We are now pleased to present

00:20:16.465 --> 00:20:21.069 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
<i>Become Jehovah’s Friend</i>
<i>—Does Jehovah Answer Prayers?</i>

00:20:24.373 --> 00:20:27.409 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Hey, Sophia, we know you’re in there.

