Please, Jehovah, make it stop!

00:20:31.580 --> 00:20:32.714 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Heh, heh, heh.

00:20:33.115 --> 00:20:34.182 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
What a loser!

00:20:34.182 --> 00:20:35.317 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Loser.

00:20:35.317 --> 00:20:36.451 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Let’s go.

00:20:36.451 --> 00:20:37.886 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Yeah, let’s get out of here.

00:21:01.343 --> 00:21:02.978 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
All right, class,

00:21:02.978 --> 00:21:05.113 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
today we’re going to discuss—

00:21:05.948 --> 00:21:08.083 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Sophia? You’re late.

00:21:08.850 --> 00:21:11.353 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
I’m sorry. Uh, I was—

00:21:11.353 --> 00:21:12.421 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Never mind.

00:21:12.421 --> 00:21:13.655 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
We’ll talk about this later.

00:21:14.022 --> 00:21:16.224 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Oooooooooo.

00:21:16.224 --> 00:21:18.593 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
OK, OK. That’s enough.

00:21:18.593 --> 00:21:20.696 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
